title: [PS3] Backgammon Blitz
description:

Backgammon's back... with a bang.

* Race against another player or a computer-controlled opponent to clear your own checker pieces off the board first.
* Graduate from pupil to master in this faithfully recreated version, or become a true show-off in Blitz mode.
* Challenge Backgammon Blitz players on PlayStation 4 from your own PlayStation 3 or PlayStation Vita system thanks to Cross-Play.
